502
00:40:00,823 --> 00:40:02,353
<b>He deserves to be called Iron Man.</b>

503
00:40:02,377 --> 00:40:04,687
<b>- Shut your mouth!
- Gosh, man.</b>

504
00:40:05,205 --> 00:40:06,205
<b>It's ominous.</b>

505
00:40:07,036 --> 00:40:08,375
<b>I have a bad feeling.</b>

506
00:40:12,118 --> 00:40:13,671
<b>Who's call are you waiting for?</b>

507
00:40:14,573 --> 00:40:16,180
<b>I'm not waiting for anyone.</b>

