510
00:40:20,978 --> 00:40:23,156
<b>- Isn't that ominous?
- Why would it be?</b>

511
00:40:23,447 --> 00:40:24,681
<b>That's super fine.</b>

512
00:40:24,705 --> 00:40:26,705
<b>- Get lost, class two.
- Kill yourself, class four.</b>

513
00:40:28,002 --> 00:40:30,002
