- Gosh.</b>

514
00:40:37,031 --> 00:40:38,031
<b>Welcome.</b>

515
00:40:38,985 --> 00:40:40,211
<b>This way, please.</b>

516
00:40:41,304 --> 00:40:44,445
<b>I'm grateful that you decided
to donate to our school.</b>

517
00:40:44,904 --> 00:40:46,008
<b>It's what I have to do.</b>

518
00:40:50,071 --> 00:40:51,071
<b>This way, ma'am.</b>

519
00:41:00,333 --> 00:41:01,546
<b>Is something up?</b>

520
00:41:09,703 --> 00:41:12,242
<b>Of all people,
I'm in the same class as him?</b>

521
00:41:35,758 --> 00:41:36,859
<b>I hear you write poems.</b>

522
00:41:37,476 --> 00:41:40,695
<b>Park Chan Hong
who won the top prize.</b>

523
00:41:41,798 --> 00:41:44,032
<b>Nice to meet you. I'm Kim Dae Yong.</b>

524
00:41:44,567 --> 00:41:45,567
<b>You know me, right?</b>

525
00:41:47,069 --> 00:41:48,992
<b>I do know you.</b>

526
00:41:51,336 --> 00:41:55,078
<b>Heo Don Hyuk is a punk as I heard.</b>

527
00:41:55,945 --> 00:41:58,145
<b>He should sit be in his chair
as soon as he's in school.</b>

528
00:42:00,610 --> 00:42:01,969
<b>How rude of him.</b>

529
00:42:09,093 --> 00:42:10,515
<b>This is supposed to be my seat.</b>

530
00:42:15,469 --> 00:42:17,695
<b>Being late on the first day
of school?</b>

531
00:42:19,223 --> 00:42:20,281
<b>You're acting cool.</b>

532
00:42:22,070 --> 00:42:24,836
<b>You're only a year older than us...</b>

533
00:42:25,408 --> 00:42:26,945
<b>so don't expect any respect.</b>

534
00:42:27,447 --> 00:42:28,447
<b>Got it?</b>

535
00:42:31,664 --> 00:42:32,864
<b>I went to school a year early.</b>

536
00:42:33,766 --> 00:42:34,766
<b>What's that?</b>

537
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:39,258
<b>We can be friends
since I went to school early.</b>

538
00:42:40,148 --> 00:42:41,148
<b>Nice to meet you.</b>

539
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,180
<b>We'll see about that.</b>

540
00:42:54,382 --> 00:42:55,382
<b>Okay.</b>

541
00:42:55,838 --> 00:42:57,125
<b>Tell me when you're done
talking.</b>

542
00:43:05,613 --> 00:43:08,047
<b>Hey, Chan Hong. Let's go
to the cafeteria.</b>

543
00:43:08,484 --> 00:43:09,484
<b>I'm buying.</b>

544
00:43:10,386 --> 00:43:11,664
<b>Lim Seong Doo!</b>

545
00:43:35,522 --> 00:43:37,327
<b>(Shin Seo Jung)</b>

546
00:43:57,197 --> 00:43:58,743
<b>That's about seven dollars.</b>

547
00:43:58,767 --> 00:44:02,091
<b>I see. I'll take this off of
your interests. You can go now.</b>

548
00:44:02,400 --> 00:44:03,400
<b>Interest?</b>

549
00:44:04,335 --> 00:44:07,784
<b>Thank you, I'll be upstairs.</b>

550
00:44:13,601 --> 00:44:16,939
<b>Have some. I picked the best snacks.</b>

551
00:44:18,610 --> 00:44:20,799
<b>Thank you. I'll enjoy them.</b>

552
00:44:21,375 --> 00:44:22,375
<b>Chan Hong.</b>

553
00:44:23,188 --> 00:44:24,985
<b>I heard you're close to Sae Yun.</b>

554
00:44:25,446 --> 00:44:29,399
<b>Me? No, I just entered the contest
with her.</b>

555
00:44:30,131 --> 00:44:31,863
<b>So we're acquaintances.</b>

556
00:44:31,887 --> 00:44:35,413
<b>Acquaintances? Many people saw you
two hang out together every day.</b>

557
00:44:37,899 --> 00:44:38,946
<b>Are you two dating?</b>

558
00:44:40,103 --> 00:44:42,501
<b>No, I'm not dating anyone.</b>

559
00:44:43,329 --> 00:44:44,329
<b>Is that so?</b>

560
00:44:45,407 --> 00:44:46,782
<b>Then introduce me to her.</b>

561
00:44:47,478 --> 00:44:49,750
<b>Timing is of the essence
with these things, right?</b>

562
00:44:50,313 --> 00:44:53,180
<b>And the thing is, I hate waiting.</b>

563
00:44:57,415 --> 00:44:59,165
<b>Okay.</b>

564
00:45:01,398 --> 00:45:02,473
<b>What's this?</b>

565
00:45:03,031 --> 00:45:04,009
<b>What?</b>

566
00:45:04,033 --> 00:45:05,196
<b>I'm leaving.</b>

567
00:45:05,220 --> 00:45:06,819
<b>Come and help me.</b>

568
00:45:10,470 --> 00:45:12,587
<b>Hey, Ninja.</b>

569
00:45:12,823 --> 00:45:16,346
<b>Why didn't you log in yesterday?</b>

570
00:45:16,517 --> 00:45:18,772
<b>Sorry, I went to bed
early last night.</b>

571
00:45:19,838 --> 00:45:22,791
<b>I lost the game
because you weren't there.</b>

572
00:45:22,845 --> 00:45:24,807
<b>I have something to tell you.</b>

573
00:45:24,831 --> 00:45:26,479
<b>- Would you come...
- Hey.</b>

574
00:45:29,290 --> 00:45:31,743
<b>- Do you want to die?
- Sorry?</b>

575
00:45:33,876 --> 00:45:36,095
<b>I'm talking to him right now.</b>

576
00:45:36,586 --> 00:45:38,046
<b>We're having a talk.</b>

577
00:45:40,322 --> 00:45:41,322
<b>Sorry.</b>

578
00:45:42,164 --> 00:45:43,418
<b>Let's talk later.</b>

579
00:45:44,063 --> 00:45:45,212
<b>Please continue.</b>

580
00:45:48,587 --> 00:45:51,046
<b>Then, you'll introduce me
to Sae Yun.</b>

581
00:45:53,416 --> 00:45:55,769
<b>Do you want anything else?
It's my treat.</b>

582
00:45:58,048 --> 00:46:01,695
<b>Do you want these? How about these?</b>

583
00:46:04,064 --> 00:46:06,120
<b>Come closer.</b>

584
00:46:06,564 --> 00:46:08,883
<b>- You talk too much.
- Stand straight.</b>

585
00:46:22,767 --> 00:46:26,321
<b>Chan Hong, do you have
some time later?</b>

586
00:46:36,555 --> 00:46:39,110
<b>Have you had that experience?</b>

587
00:46:43,501 --> 00:46:46,384
<b>You've seen something scary...</b>

588
00:46:48,047 --> 00:46:52,219
<b>and if I turn a blind eye, it can
pass like it was nothing.</b>

589
00:46:55,243 --> 00:46:58,821
<b>Me acting like I noticed it won't
make a difference...</b>

590
00:47:00,220 --> 00:47:02,414
<b>so it's something scary that
I want to avoid.</b>

591
00:47:03,197 --> 00:47:04,658
<b>Do you get it?</b>

592
00:47:09,485 --> 00:47:11,063
<b>What would you...</b>

593
00:47:11,697 --> 00:47:14,040
<b>do if you saw things like that?</b>

594
00:47:17,431 --> 00:47:20,462
<b>Should I confront them
even though they are scary...</b>

595
00:47:21,516 --> 00:47:24,564
<b>or let bygones be bygones?</b>

596
00:47:28,870 --> 00:47:30,614
<b>If it was me...</b>

597
00:47:33,266 --> 00:47:35,500
<b>I would like it
if you wouldn't get hurt.</b>

598
00:47:37,290 --> 00:47:39,622
<b>I don't know
what you're talking about...</b>

599
00:47:40,634 --> 00:47:41,810
<b>but whatever it is...</b>

600
00:47:43,579 --> 00:47:45,755
<b>I want you to make the choice
that makes you happier.</b>

601
00:47:47,344 --> 00:47:49,291
<b>You said it doesn't change anything.</b>

602
00:47:51,322 --> 00:47:52,661
<b>Maybe you're right.</b>

603
00:47:54,032 --> 00:47:56,742
<b>I also want to be happier.</b>

604
00:47:58,556 --> 00:48:00,329
<b>I don't want to...</b>

605
00:48:00,946 --> 00:48:03,281
<b>- introduce you to him.
- Wow, Chan Hong.</b>

606
00:48:04,087 --> 00:48:05,614
<b>You're so smart.</b>

607
00:48:06,204 --> 00:48:07,485
<b>It's nothing.</b>

608
00:48:12,314 --> 00:48:13,434
<b>Hey.</b>

609
00:48:23,165 --> 00:48:24,915
<b>Please, let this go.</b>

610
00:48:40,039 --> 00:48:42,362
<b>Hey, do I look good to you?</b>

611
00:48:42,993 --> 00:48:44,760
<b>It's not like that.</b>

612
00:48:46,508 --> 00:48:47,555
<b>Right?</b>

613
00:48:48,157 --> 00:48:51,544
<b>Someone saw you two being close
in a pizza place.</b>

614
00:48:51,829 --> 00:48:53,748
<b>There's no way you took me for
a pushover.</b>

615
00:49:00,118 --> 00:49:01,510
<b>You have until this evening.</b>

616
00:49:02,517 --> 00:49:04,040
<b>If you ignore me this time...</b>

617
00:49:05,336 --> 00:49:08,056
<b>I'll make you piss your pants every
time you even think about school.</b>

618
00:49:21,055 --> 00:49:23,274
<b>A cafe in downtown at 7 p.m. today.</b>

619
00:49:23,962 --> 00:49:26,548
<b>If you don't come up with results,
I'm going to kill you.</b>

620
00:49:42,173 --> 00:49:43,259
<b>Sae Yun.</b>

621
00:49:44,790 --> 00:49:46,477
<b>Don't come here.</b>

622
00:49:46,501 --> 00:49:47,932
<b>- Go to the pizza place...
- Hey.</b>

623
00:49:48,314 --> 00:49:49,361
<b>What is it?</b>

624
00:49:51,454 --> 00:49:54,040
<b>- Why did you want to see me here?
- I know.</b>

625
00:49:54,064 --> 00:49:57,169
<b>- This place stinks. Let's get out.
- Are you okay?</b>

626
00:49:57,594 --> 00:49:58,792
<b>What happened to your face?</b>

627
00:49:59,868 --> 00:50:01,053
<b>What's going on?</b>

628
00:50:01,836 --> 00:50:03,657
<b>It's nothing.</b>

629
00:50:03,961 --> 00:50:05,780
<b>- Let's get out of here.
- Okay.</b>

630
00:50:06,286 --> 00:50:08,600
<b>I also have something...</b>

631
00:50:13,782 --> 00:50:14,989
<b>Chan Hong?</b>

632
00:50:16,907 --> 00:50:18,765
<b>Yes, Dae Yong.</b>

633
00:50:21,798 --> 00:50:25,026
<b>I heard you were close. Are you here
to take a break from studying?</b>

634
00:50:25,882 --> 00:50:29,451
<b>Chan Hong told me multiple times
that he would introduce me to you.</b>

635
00:50:30,086 --> 00:50:32,046
<b>I didn't think we would bump into
each other here.</b>

636
00:50:33,407 --> 00:50:36,031
<b>Hey, you should have
given me a heads up.</b>

637
00:50:36,055 --> 00:50:38,185
<b>I would have dressed better.</b>

638
00:50:39,493 --> 00:50:42,711
<b>What is up with this place?</b>

639
00:50:43,306 --> 00:50:45,990
<b>I'm sorry. He's never dated anyone.</b>

640
00:50:46,014 --> 00:50:49,139
<b>I guess you're right. It must be
because he never dated anyone.</b>

641
00:50:53,269 --> 00:50:54,708
<b>(Mom)</b>

642
00:50:55,228 --> 00:50:56,713
<b>I think your phone's ringing.</b>

643
00:50:57,539 --> 00:50:58,900
<b>You should take it outside.</b>

644
00:51:04,704 --> 00:51:06,165
<b>I'll go answer this quickly.</b>

645
00:51:12,712 --> 00:51:14,118
<b>Let's have a seat.</b>

646
00:51:27,586 --> 00:51:28,827
<b>Mom, what is it?</b>

647
00:51:28,990 --> 00:51:32,558
<b>What do you mean why?
You told me to call you on time!</b>

648
00:51:56,048 --> 00:51:57,838
<b>My mom told me to come home...</b>

649
00:51:58,806 --> 00:52:00,241
<b>so I have to hurry back.</b>

650
00:52:02,415 --> 00:52:03,640
<b>See you tomorrow.</b>

651
00:52:26,087 --> 00:52:27,928
<b>It was difficult to be normal.</b>

652
00:52:33,251 --> 00:52:35,482
<b>I was below average.</b>

653
00:52:47,798 --> 00:52:50,276
<b>- I'm home.
- Are you here?</b>

654
00:52:50,327 --> 00:52:52,131
<b>- Have you eaten?
- Yes.</b>

655
00:52:52,822 --> 00:52:55,163
<b>- Okay.
- Chan Hong.</b>

656
00:52:55,564 --> 00:52:57,230
<b>Show me your face.</b>

657
00:52:57,254 --> 00:53:00,493
<b>- Take off your hoodie.
- It's nothing.</b>

658
00:53:02,244 --> 00:53:05,898
<b>Chan Hong, are you not going to
tell me what's going on?</b>

659
00:53:06,087 --> 00:53:09,885
<b>- What happened to your face?
- I said it's nothing!</b>

660
00:53:15,032 --> 00:53:16,319
<b>You...</b>

661
00:53:16,498 --> 00:53:18,537
<b>Come back out here.</b>

662
00:53:18,561 --> 00:53:20,414
<b>What are you going to do
inside there?</b>

663
00:53:23,056 --> 00:53:24,455
<b>Let's leave him be.</b>

664
00:53:25,461 --> 00:53:27,630
<b>Turn a blind eye for him.</b>

665
00:53:29,422 --> 00:53:31,660
<b>His face...</b>

666
00:53:57,500 --> 00:53:59,826
<b>(Reminiscence of Kim Sung Ho)</b>

667
00:54:26,644 --> 00:54:29,540
<b>We weren't even dating,
but why am I crying?</b>

668
