00:55:58,130 --> 00:55:59,330
<b>Where is...</b>

671
00:55:59,747 --> 00:56:00,951
<b>her mobile phone?</b>

672
00:56:04,287 --> 00:56:05,466
<b>Hey.</b>

673
00:56:07,802 --> 00:56:09,898
<b>Why do you have so much money?</b>

674
00:56:17,271 --> 00:56:19,763
<b>Don't do that.
